title: How to get your toxic Senna adc and Karma support to shut the hell up.
body: Get a double kill in their lane then type "REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE UNINSTALL MASTER YI YOU ARE SO USELESSSSSSSSS REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!"  I did that and they were all like... "shutup" you know when a little kid looks down embarrassed and is all like "shutup". Yea.... it works.....
